## Additional Terms for Network Use

As this project modifies RustDesk Server (HBBS) which is licensed under AGPL-3.0,
the following additional terms apply:

If you run a modified version of this software on a server and let users 
interact with it remotely through a network, you must make the complete 
source code of your modified version available to those users.

The modifications to RustDesk HBBS are located in the `hbbs-patch/` directory
and must remain open source under AGPL-3.0.

Full AGPL-3.0 license text: https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html

